The following code
```
module top(
    input logic a,
    output logic b
);
function automatic void inv(
    input w_in,
    output w_out
);
    w_out = ~w_in;
endfunction


always_comb
inv(
    .w_out(b),
    .w_in(a)

);

endmodule
```
